{
  "name": "Locus: Syzygy (Moon)",
  "type": "equipment",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em>(Requires attunement by a creature. The properties of this item are affixed to the rod, wand, staff, jewelry, or armor.)</em></p><p><em>This item is a @UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.rules.JournalEntry.nniVtdJB1oyk5Sa3]{locus} and can be combined with other <strong>Loci </strong>per the @UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.rules.JournalEntry.nniVtdJB1oyk5Sa3.JournalEntryPage.zI0VWGKnYZqz6sKd]{Combining Loci} rules.</em></p><p>This relic was found affixed to one end of an ancient rod. The half of the rod associated with this Locus was tinted silver.</p><p>While attuned the relic merges magically merges with a <strong>rod, wand, staff, jewelry, or armor </strong>of your choice. This can be done during a short or long rest, requires 10 minutes to complete and it upon completion the item takes on a silvery hue and sheen. Once completed, the item becomes magical for the purpose of overcoming resistances.</p><p><strong>Effect: </strong>While on the material plane on Materia from Dusk to Dawn, if the item this locus is affixed to has charges, the current and maximum number of charges is increased by your proficiency bonus. Furthermore, when you hit a creature or it fails a saving throw against you they must make an Intelligence saving throw. On a failure they treat you as invisible until the end of your next turn.</p><table><thead><tr><td>Character Level</td><td>Save DC</td></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>1-4</td><td>12</td></tr><tr><td>5-8</td><td>14</td></tr><tr><td>9-12</td><td>16</td></tr><tr><td>13-16</td><td>18</td></tr><tr><td>17-20</td><td>20</td></tr></tbody></table><p><strong>Special:</strong> This Locus is dormant if the user is not also attuned to the <strong>@UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.magic-items.Item.NZC6FpoRO0P4sZeY]{Locus: Syzygy (Sun)}</strong>.</p><p>If you are not on Materia or not on the Material Plane, then you only benefit from the first bonus granted by both the <strong>@UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.magic-items.Item.NZC6FpoRO0P4sZeY]{Locus: Syzygy (Sun})</strong> and <strong>@UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.magic-items.Item.d4kJXuBWLAgCCWTp]{Locus: Syzygy (Moon)}</strong>.</p>",
